    "POS-Tag on ChER (chemical entity recognizer) performed by Navvaro et al.",
    "claims to improve the performance of NER compared to ChemSpot and MetaboliNER [74].",
    "As shown in Figure 7, cleaning is also popularly used by NER researchers to clean raw data.",
    "Raw data from generic websites contain many HTML and XML tags, advertisements, and menus [75].",
    "Raw data emails contain signatures and attachments."
